# .file-size-allowlist
#
# Pre-existing files that exceed the 750-LOC hard cap.
# These are grandfathered — they existed before the LOC standard was enforced.
# Remove an entry from this list only AFTER splitting the file into sub-modules.
#
# Do NOT add new files here. Any new file over 750 LOC must be split before merge.
# Run: node scripts/check-file-size.mjs
#
# Format: one relative path per line (forward slashes, from repo root).
